extendedInfo.description: Travel through space in a spectacular wormhole through Nebula!Features:- Smooth 3D GPU acceleration- Tablet support- Moving Star fields- Parallax effects with homescreen movement (depending on launcher)- Battery saver mode- Turbo mode (high speed nebula)- This free version has Blue+Green Wormhole and Nebula (low concentration), and star fields.FULL/PAID VERSION FEATURES:- Full Color Nebula and twice the Nebula types- Wormhole color options (including multicolor and rapid changes)- Wormhole camera centering speed options- Various optional objects including asteroids, planets, satellites, etc..- Ability to turn off the wormhole if you only want the Nebula- Nebula concentration settings for performance tweaking or eye candy- Nebula color range options (Deep orange, Red+Blue, Violet, Deep colors, etc..)- Nebula Speed setting. Very slow to Warp Speed!- FPS limiterNote: The screenshots are from the Full version. You can sample the full version Nebula at high concentration by enabling the "Full version nebula demo" option in the Wallpaper settings.After installation, the wallpaper can be found by going to the Homescreen and pressing Menu -> Wallpaper -> Live Wallpapers. There is no application icon.Enjoy!
